commit message:
Updated target API level to Android 4.4.

Updated version number for the next release.

Code cleanup and optimization.

Modified color scheme - there are now 'empty' cells to indicate time ranges before and after the current known cycles and predicted period days now also display days with white text.

Merge pull request #12 from larjona/Spanish

Add Spanish translation

Code cleanup

More uniform translations

Added new overlay for future predicted ovulation
Remove unnecessary typeface setting for 'current' cells
